<br>
Ethereal Light<br>
Level 58<br>
Mana  525<br>
<br>
This spell heals a single target for 1600 hitpoints for 525 mana. This is an upgrade to Divine Light which heals 910 for 350 Mana.<br>
<br>
5 sec casting time<br>
<br>
*****************<br>
Ethereal Elixir<br>
Level 60<br>
Mana 1050 <br>
<br>
This spell heals each person in the Cleric's group by 300 hitpoints per tick for 4 ticks. This provides a total of 1200 hitpoints healing to each person in the group for only 1050 mana.<br>
<br>
Casting time 5.5 secs <br>
